block_list.title: Video Tutorial
block_list.body: Today we are learning how to fold an Icosahedral Skeleton by Miyuki Kawamura. This model is really pretty and I know you'll enjoy it. Please find the time stamp of the tutorial below. It's to help you jump through the tutorial quickly. 00:09 How to fold the Module 02:21 Module folding Time-lapse 02:40 Assembling the Base of the Model 04:35 Assembling the Middle of the Model 06:34 Assembling the Top of the Model Thanks for watching! Wilson Lee@Heap Art
